        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: add Namespace Compute instance provider",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- add `namespace-instance` (`namespace-compute`) as a direct Linux SSH lease provider backed by `nsc`\n- preserve the existing `namespace` alias for Namespace Devbox\n- add per-lease SSH keys, proxy-backed SSH/sync/run, tenant-scoped ownership, guarded rollback/recovery, TTL handling, and cleanup\n- add trusted config/env/flags, provider docs, generated matrix metadata, doctor coverage, and guarded live smoke coverage\n\nCloses https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/296\n\n## Verification\n\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --stream-engine-output` (clean; no actionable findings)\n- `go test -race ./...`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `go build -trimpath -o bin/crabbox ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `go test ./internal/providers/namespaceinstance ./internal/cli ./internal/providers/all` after rebase onto `origin/main`\n- `scripts/check-docs.sh`\n- `node scripts/generate-provider-matrix.mjs --check`\n- `bash -n scripts/live-smoke.sh scripts/live-doctor-smoke.sh`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `CRABBOX_LIVE=1 CRABBOX_LIVE_PROVIDERS=namespace-instance scripts/live-smoke.sh`\n  - exact-head commit `5164e88eb564871f7471e99aea773386addcf852`\n  - lease `cbx_eb7463b020d6`, Namespace instance `vrko5vbe5i8ng`\n  - provisioned 4x8 Linux instance, verified SSH and cache inspection\n  - synced 891 files / 12.7 MiB and ran `crabbox-live-ok`\n  - released successfully; post-smoke Crabbox-owned inventory count: 0\n\n## Review follow-up\n\n- preserve provider `leased`/`ready` states so claimless cleanup uses normal expiry semantics\n- only invoke `nsc destroy` after inventory confirms matching tenant and lease ownership labels\n- treat a successfully queried but already-missing instance as an idempotent release and remove only the local claim/key\n- confirmed installed `nsc v0.0.522` supports `create --output json`; exact-head live creation also exercises this path\n\n## Security / configuration\n\n- no new repository secrets\n- `nsc` endpoint, region, keychain, CLI path, and volume attachments are accepted only from trusted user config, environment, or explicit flags\n- destructive operations require tenant-matching Crabbox ownership labels\n",
